     Chem. Phys. 2009 356(1-3), 98-109
     doi.org/10.1016/j.chemphys.2008.10.036
  3. Stoychev, G.L.; Auer, A.A.; Neese, F.
     Automatic Generation of Auxiliary Basis Sets
